ng.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" />. Also, the super golem is really big, just fyi.<BR />ic: *I leap down and knock you to the ground with a foot* (ooc: you are a matoran, right?)<BR />*a green glow surrounds my axe, then the glow disappears and a ball of fire suddenly appears overhead*<BR />(smiles) so, matoran, looks like this is going to end even before it started! This is going to feel good, I have kept a bit of a... grudge, you might say, against matoran. </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />*smiles back* Oh, this is not over yet, pal.<BR /><BR />*begins growing brighter and brighter, so bright that it starts to blind you for a few seconds*<BR /><BR />*I run away at the chance, wondering why I am glowing, when suddenly I start having flashbacks to Karda Nui...*<BR /><BR />Light... Pain, light, fused into me..... Light....<BR /><BR />*I keep running, clutching my staff*<BR /><BR />-Maktor- </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />*I notice your distraction and fire a blast of energy at you, knocking you to the ground*<BR />*I begin charging my energy* </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />*I stumble back up, and begin glowing even brighter than before as you charge your energy, and I face you*<BR /><BR />My destiny... I can feel it...<BR /><BR />*I keep charging up as you do the same*<BR /><BR />-Maktor- </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />ooc: If we're both charging up, should we do a time-lapse so our next posts won't be *Voidarix charges up more* *Maktor charges up more* <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /> </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />OoC: Ok, you go ahead. <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /><BR /><BR />-Maktor-</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />ooc: okay<BR />ic: *after a few minutes, I let go 